<div class="email-container">
    <h1>Hi, <%= @user.email %>!</h1>

    <h2>Profile Updated by Admin</h2>

    <p>We wanted to let you know that your profile details on <strong>Fotobook</strong> have been updated by one of our administrators.</p>

    <div class="highlight">
      <p><strong>What might have changed?</strong></p>
      <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin: 0;">
        <li>Display name or profile photo</li>
        <li>Bio or personal information</li>
        <li>Account status or privileges</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p>If you did not request these changes or have any concerns, please contact our support team immediately.</p>

    <p class="footer-note">
      You can review your updated profile by logging into your account.
    </p>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= Time.current.year %> Fotobook. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
